OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUniversal credit boost for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers takes effect       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Budget changes that boost the income of
OL,6, some working people on universal credit
OL,7, come into force from now, the          
OL,8, government has announced.              
OL,10,FWorkers will now take home 8p more of  
OL,11,Fany extra pound earned, owing to a     
OL,12,Fshift in the so-called taper rate.     
OL,14,FChancellor Rishi Sunak said in         
OL,15,FOctober's Budget that the change would 
OL,16,Ftake effect "within weeks" and no later
OL,17,Fthan December 1.                       
OL,19,FThe policy was announced amid debate   
OL,20,Fover the benefit's suitability.        
